.Dd $Mdocdate: December 13 2020 $
.Dt PORTMK 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm portmk
.Nd build automation
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl e Ar var
.Op Fl f Ar flag
.Op Fl m Ar flag
.Ar method
.Ar args ...
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
utility executes the build process with the given
.Ar method .
.Sh OPTIONS
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl e Ar var
Export
.Ar var
to the environment.
.It Fl f Ar flag
Pass the
.Ar flag
to the portmk.
.It Fl m Ar flag
Pass the
.Ar flag
to the build tool.
.El
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width XXXXXXXXXXXXXX -compat
.It Pa $PORTS/mk/meth
Directory which includes all supported methods.
.El
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Ex -std
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr mkutils 1 ,
.Xr portsys 1
